RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.BRANCH_CODE, B.BRANCH_NAME FROM STTM_CORE_BRANCH A, STTM_CORE_BRANCH B WHERE B.BRANCH_CODE = A.BRANCH_CODE AND B.ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND (A.HO_EXRATE = 'N' OR B.BRANCH_CODE = (SELECT HO_BRANCH FROM STTM_CORE_BANK))

SELECT CCY1,CCY_NAME1,CCY2, CCY_NAME2,QUOTATION,SPREAD_DEF,MULTIPLIER FROM (SELECT A.CCY1 CCY1, B.CCY_NAME CCY_NAME1, A.CCY2 CCY2, C.CCY_NAME CCY_NAME2, A.QUOTATION QUOTATION, A.SPREAD_DEFN SPREAD_DEF, A.POINTS_MULTIPLIER MULTIPLIER FROM CYTMS_CCY_PAIR_DEFN A, CYTM_CCY_DEFN B, CYTM_CCY_DEFN C WHERE A.CCY1 = B.CCY_CODE AND A.CCY2 = C.CCY_CODE AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.RECORD_STAT = 'O')
SELECT CCY_RATE_TYPE, CCY_RATE_TYPE_DESC FROM CYTMS_RATE_TYPE WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y'
